HEADWORD: Inaction
<hw>In*ac"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in</ets>. not + <ets>action</ets>: cf. <ets>inaction</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Lack of action or activity; forbearance from labor; idleness; rest;
inertness.</def> <rj><au>Berkeley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
